{"tid":881973,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"金融黑洞!【美股戰報】憂中美貿易戰升級 道指高低波幅近900點","createTime":"2018-10-30T00:35:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T02:26:12.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2bf30d906186a04f05c5d3e46e4559320eaab8","tid":881973,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:35:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181030/58851544\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851544&d=w7oyhniWVZMVzTooW2c9B7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8776bdbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181030%2F58851544&h=b5d1032e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181030/58851544</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n彭博通訊社周一報道，中美元首下月會談若<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無</span>突破，美國將宣佈向所有進口中國貨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">加徵</span>關稅，消息影響美股三大指數<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">低收</span>。道瓊斯工業平均指數收<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跌</span>245.39點，跌幅0.99%，報24442點。標普500指數收<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跌</span>17.44點，跌幅0.66%，報2641點。納斯達克綜合指數收跌116.92點，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跌</span>幅1.63%，報7050點。<br />\n道指早段曾漲超過350點後，然後<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">倒跌</span>超過500點，全日高低波幅接近900點，最終收<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跌</span>245點。<br />\n英國財政大臣夏文達（Philip Hammond）表示，在線服務對英國稅收系統的可持續性和公平性帶來真正的挑戰。因此，英國將引入數字服務稅。這項稅收將隻針對科技巨頭的英國收入，而不是初創公司。這項稅收不是針對消費者的網上銷售稅，數字服務稅將只由全球營收至少5億歐元的盈利公司支付，預料數字服務稅將於2020年4月生效。<br />\n受消息影響，亞馬遜<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重挫</span>6.33%，市值蒸發超500億美元。阿里巴巴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴跌</span>6.64%。"},{"pid":"80a8760788f89caf3e1eb8270eea1eb93f65b4b7","tid":881973,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"一陣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56caad27cb73f4dd4461b7f235133e8eda34ae8a","tid":881973,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a8760788f89caf3e1eb8270eea1eb93f65b4b7","tid":881973,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"一陣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下試 2000 點 !"},{"pid":"068e9d2d4ddb0659ff8b97e9934635f39d0847c4","tid":881973,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"尋日都係靠大笨象頂住先唔洗跌"},{"pid":"63e495d4d1108038f00beff754a1e765508c4024","tid":881973,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:40:05.000Z","msg":"好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449aad9b28c1be5b350b5f5f4ece2be37ac81ce0","tid":881973,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T00:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港己死 !</span>"},{"pid":"280c388845c6a1baf40ab1b770935e6b29b045d4","tid":881973,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:54:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f6b50592ae1aee121052fe5a05968ced8d511b8","tid":881973,"uid":65346,"li